{"tid":693731,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"幾時開始個個睇戲都睇到咁無品","createTime":"2018-06-07T17:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T13:44:33.000Z","uid":112099,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7d4c78fc896df1ac8b6e19e2fd34761457f1d6c7","tid":693731,"uid":112099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T17:00:02.000Z","msg":"睇侏羅紀隔離條港女見隻恐龍郁一下就叫一下<br />\n全程都係度嗯嗯呀呀啊同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">尖叫</span></span><br />\n另一邊情侶殊鳩完佢地仲屌番轉頭愈講愈大聲<br />\n後一排廢中不停討論劇情<br />\n有小妹妹不停大聲講野<br />\n又有人玩足全程膠袋<br />\n仲有前面隔5分鐘開一次電話覆wtsapp<br />\n<br />\n最撚奇怪係 <br />\n成個戲院好似得我覺得有問題咁完全無人開聲屌<br />\n<br />\n又唔知幾時開始係套戲未開始有聲同演員講野之前d人都唔會停口<br />\n<br />\n其實大家應該由細都知睇戲係應該靜同唔好騷擾到人<br />\n點解今時今日大個咗又會變成咁？<br />\n好多做呢d閪野既閪人都係後生仔女或者廿中廿尾咁既情侶 <br />\n到底係乜野令你地變到咁？"},{"pid":"914f4eb482ab9a42352b6f9469efc7619ccd0894","tid":693731,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T17:04:21.000Z","msg":"恐龍叫姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53322575a1a28a68137bdd490e313615e95b4e1","tid":693731,"uid":112099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"914f4eb482ab9a42352b6f9469efc7619ccd0894","tid":693731,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T17:04:21.000Z","msg":"恐龍叫姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T17:06:17.000Z","msg":"恐龍叫都好聽過佢叫 痴撚線"},{"pid":"0ffe15315c3f1f2678e5e27aaf78e1a9b9ba8e6c","tid":693731,"uid":25003,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b53322575a1a28a68137bdd490e313615e95b4e1","tid":693731,"uid":112099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"914f4eb482ab9a42352b6f9469efc7619ccd0894","tid":693731,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T17:04:21.000Z","msg":"恐龍叫姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T17:06:17.000Z","msg":"恐龍叫都好聽過佢叫 痴撚線"},"c